column4: Seattle is the better team and should win this game most of the time, but the line has drifted past what the underlying numbers support. In betting terms, that usually means one thing: hold your nose, take the unsexy home dog with +7.5, and let the favorite win the game without having to blow anyone out to justify the price.

Classic division rivalry spot where the total feels inflated. The Chargers defense has strangled opponents at home, and the Raiders offense struggles on the road. Look for a grind-it-out game that stays Under 44.5.
